version_description:
It is now possible to pay with Maestro card.
Improve update of station's availabilities information.

New in your « Vélo’v officiel » app!

You can now see the duration of your journey in progress thanks to the chrono included on the map!
You need a break? Turn on the bluetooth of your smartphone and connect it to the « Vélo’v officiel » app: you can now take a short break and secure your Vélo'v with its electronic lock.

New in your « Vélo’v officiel » app!

You can now see the duration of your journey in progress thanks to the chrono included on the map!
You need a break? Turn on the bluetooth of your smartphone and connect it to the « Vélo’v officiel » app: you can now take a short break and secure your Vélo'v with its electronic lock. (all Vélo'v will be gradually equipped with an electronic lock in the coming weeks).

- Geovelo itineraries
- Long term subscription display
- User statistics
- Bug fixes
We are regularly updating the app to improve your experience. This new version improves stability and brings new features to guide you to your destination
